# ðŸŽ™ Python Voice Assistant AI

A voice-controlled AI assistant built using Python that can recognize speech commands and perform tasks like opening websites and playing music.

---

##  Features

-  Wake word detection ("Jarvis")
-  Open websites (Google, YouTube, LinkedIn, GitHub)
-  Play songs from a predefined music list
-  Text-to-Speech response system
-  Speech Recognition using Google API

